{"tid":730441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有線新聞：內地客減少 非內地客增加。阿根廷遊客：香港像日本一樣文明，而中國完全相反。","createTime":"2018-07-05T11:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:46:37.000Z","uid":112551,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d91a467343d272b2a9c046a7f012ef34bac5b03","tid":730441,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"【訪港旅客比去年同期跌7.4%】<br />\n【內地客減少　非內地客增加】<br />\n<br />\n上半年訪港旅客比去年同期下跌 7.4%，主要因為內地客減少，其他地區的旅客反而增加。<br />\n<br />\n有外國遊客稱，歐洲的恐襲威脅令他卻步，改到亞洲旅遊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/195305_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F195305_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG&h=6e00776d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/195306_02b316b5cb5067f2795e9667a3985816.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F195306_02b316b5cb5067f2795e9667a3985816.PNG&h=c79ebedc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/195307_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F195307_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG&h=672c5146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/195308_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F195308_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG&h=39b9965c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/537428633115876/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F537428633115876%2F&d=wz%2FZjKwIRaCioXb8dQfv8f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=2de484d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/537428633115876/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係兩年前, 但成日聽到人話外國人眼中香港同中國無分別, 想分享比大家.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10ef6de64ec9f451689d7be876ab265e351b5a7","tid":730441,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b8921b5143323a235832aa267e2548b0eb24ab","tid":730441,"uid":61625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96acde831fdf4da8da7335139e174eb3b942ba19","tid":730441,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"有線咁就lum掂左連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估計未來將有大量吹奏有線post"},{"pid":"c06d60e3bc6e254d5404ac36878bbbaa3a9bf806","tid":730441,"uid":128972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:34:01.000Z","msg":"唔同國家好難一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0500333f7deca21d97822ba7503417cbd241d240","tid":730441,"uid":41205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"五毛不敢面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44881592348a1e2f6e30c90fac936b263e148dc","tid":730441,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=